Hi to all<br />
i have a problem with a simple scattered chart: the x values (categories) are poorly managed with overlapping. I post you simple code (from a modified version of 33chartcreate-scatter.php). I've test this script with last version of PHPExcel. What is wrong??<br />
<br />
Here is the code:<br />
<pre><code>&lt;?php

